<TEXT>
two dogs owned by irish film producer 
kevin mcclory attacked a retired california judge near her vacation 
home biting her more than 50 times her husband said sunday 
richard rogan said his wife 72yearold mary goode rogan a 
former los angeles county superior court judge is recovering in a 
hospital after undergoing surgery for wounds suffered in the july 5 
attack 
rogan of burbank calif said mcclory has disappeared with the 
dogs both boxers despite a court order that the animals be 
destroyed 
rogan spoke with reporters and his remarks were carried by the 
news agency ireland international 
mcclory whose credits include the 1965 james bond movie 
thunderball has lived since november in a fiveroom apartment 
at the rogans summer home st clerans according to rogan 
the only response to telephone calls to mcclorys apartment was 
an answering machine 
police in county galway said an order that the dogs be destroyed 
was issued wednesday at loughrea district court but mcclory did 
not attend the hearing 
we are told the dogs have been taken away for training said 
one officer who was not identified in line with police regulations 
we have tried to contact mr mcclory but we have been told he is 
away seeking film locations 
mcclorys wife elisabeth is the daughter of vincent obrien 
one of irelands leading horse trainers a spokesman for the 
obrien family who spoke with the condition he not be identified 
said sunday he believed mcclory was somewhere in the west of 
ireland looking for film locations 
rogan said his wife was attacked while walking in a meadow near 
the house in county galway in eastern ireland 
